column1: Every round new Investors (VCs) can invest 365€ per person into the organization, receiving newly minted tokens in exchange. The number of VCs in each rounds follows the fibonacci sequence. For every round 30% additional tokens are minted into the community pool. 75% of the euro investments go into the investment pool, 25% of the euro investments go into the admin pool (maintaining the organization). The first 25000 tokens are registered capital for the GmbH, being split into a founders exit share (curr. 15%) and a DAO (85%) treasury, which will be handed over to the DAO after leaving the German jurisdiction.
